&lt;li&gt;Work as part of the design department and with the Code team to help shape the C++/C# interface.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Identify and fix memory and performance issues.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Help define code standards, work processes, and look after the overall code quality.&lt;/li&gt;
